Samsung Galaxy S7 For Dummies (2016) (Pdf & Epub) Gooner

Publisher: John Wiley & Sons Inc (27 May 2016)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 111927995X
ISBN-13: 978-1119279952

Get the most out of your Galaxy S7 Make fun videos and take amazing photos Personalize your phone and keep it secure
Set up & have fun with your Samsung S7

If you just scored yourself a Samsung Galaxy S7 and don't quite know where to start, you're in good hands! Packed with easy-to-follow guidance and tons of tips and trick, this fun and accessible guide helps you discover just how fast and easy it is to use your new smartphone.

Inside... Text your friends and family Send and receive email Manage your contacts Share pictures Play games like a pro Make sense of maps Enjoy music and videos Manage your calendar Secure your phone
